txt.en: You learned from some of the captives you rescued that there are ambassadors from each of the major Dunlending clans and the half-orcs of Isengard within Torsbury. You should defeat the ambassadors.
The Dunlending and half-orc ambassadors may be found throughout the encampment at Torsbury.\n\nYou should defeat the ambassadors from the Dunlending clans and the half-orcs.
Thane Tordag is at his encampment, north of the road between Torsbury and Stoke.\n\nYou should return to Thane Tordag and let him know that you have defeated the leaders of the clans at Torsbury.
